Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fqWKjS9rTDk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfqWKjS9rTDk&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=f37dd8ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fqWKjS9rTDk</a>"},{"pid":"8597d4226bdb2a459ee9876148309e0a27c5a137","tid":1237834,"uid":157938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:53:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=996f216d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span>"},{"pid":"c490fbafc7f3c9e78642bbadde6a64430585b40c","tid":1237834,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:58:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xBZ43nu2d3I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxBZ43nu2d3I&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=f3e32b19\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xBZ43nu2d3I</a>"},{"pid":"d2cd9a09f8df694c3014ebe67b4ac928785a4baa","tid":1237834,"uid":207975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"推"}]}